item.title: Lv49 Requesting Note Page Bingo--Can Reciprocate!
item.content:encoded: Felina, Lv49, Epic Village. I need a Note Page Bingo to obtain Anonymous. I have a Note Page in reserve myself, and would be more than happy to tag the person back tomorrow if that's what they want, and their village doesn't have a big Peacetime bonus. (Wiki Redux is showing as +2 right now, so if that's where the character you want Bingo'd is, that's certainly doable.)
